title: kokona_haruka_(yandere_simulator)
body:
Kokona Haruka is a character from the sandbox game [[Yandere Simulator]]. Recognized for her [[large breasts]] and [[purple hair|purple]] [[twin drills]], she is considered a rival of [[ayano aishi|Yandere-chan]] due her crush on [[Senpai_(yandere_simulator)|Senpai]].

Despite this characters appearance being similar to the popular [[UTAU]], [[Kasane Teto]], this was unintentional as the original base model of the character was simply a [[mikumikudance|3D model]] of Teto.
